File-aware routing:
- `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md` edits -> `documentation-standards` then `format-lint-audit`
- `package.json`, `format.sh`, `scripts/*.mjs` edits -> `task-planner` and `lint-fix`
- `.work/*.md` reports -> `content-scaffold` and `doc-validator`
- Canonical skill path: `.claude/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`

Keep diffs minimal and repository conventions intact.
